skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: fitness facts
des:
This skill contains some fitness facts targeted for any one who either is already a fitness enthusiast or want to become one.
These are some of interesting facts that you might want to know. 

Learn and Test your Knowledge from these Fitness Facts. Do You Know them All?

You can invoke the skill by saying
Eg. Alexa, open Fitness Facts and tell me a fact. or Alexa, open Fitness Facts and give me some information.

Disclaimer:The information in this skill is provided for informational and educational purposes only.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
